      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-03-17T00:33:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "#1 is fine by me, but the SQ package will probably need to be outside of Run (but don\u0027t move it just yet, TODO is fine).\n\n#2 loading config is cheap, even if from datastore, and in most cases, you\u0027ll get it from Redis. So, I wouldn\u0027t care to optimize that.\nSo, IMO, we should go this route.\n\n(i\u0027m ok leaving this CL as is, and modifying in the next CL)",
